race.comment: VERY BEST BUDDY (1) has been out of the placings at his last couple but on the winners' heels when placing three back (20.06) in a Grade 5 at this track. Key player on best and expected to bounce back. NICK'S MATE (2) turned in a solid run last start over 318m at Dubbo finishing 5th and beaten only 3.5 lengths (18.95). Some good form is emerging from his last run. Key player if finds best. QUICK EDITION (4) is a fast beginner who has shown good improvement at his last two starts, the latest scoring at this track over 431m. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Leading player again. LEKTRA BELLA (7) is a last-start placegetter with solid claims again.
